title: Migos Chill With Dead Presidents in New Video for “Deadz” Featuring 2 Chainz

organizations.name: c u l t u r e

text:
In continuing their onslaught of material in support of C U L T U R E , Migos unleash the official music video for “Deadz” featuring 2 Chainz. The clip was directed by Daps, who also manned the trio’s highly entertaining “T-Shirt” shoot.
We in turn find the Migos members decked out in their designer favorites, counting up in a luxe mansion. An orchestra is providing musical accompaniment out front, while inside are caskets filled with dead presidents.
Yeah, you’ll want to press play above to soak all of this in.
